  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">SHARE: Supporting the Hardest to Reach Through Basic Education  : Aloghar (Lighthouse) - Mainstreaming</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To mainstream around 45,000 children into the government primary schools or any other schools.Overall objective: Increased empowerment, enhanced literacy, self-reliance and better social integration of disadvantaged and hardest to reach childrenSpecific objective: Hardest to reach children enjoy their right to quality basic education at Aloghar pre- and primary level and equal opportunities of being mainstreamed into government or private schools</narrative>
  </description>
